Class Program

java.lang.Object
ca.openosp.openo.commn.model.AbstractModel<Integer>
ca.openosp.openo.PMmodule.model.Program
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class Program extends AbstractModel<Integer>
This is the object class that relates to the program table. Any customizations belong here. Entity implementation class for Entity: Program Represents a program in the system.
